<section xmlns="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/dc-library" xmlns:codified="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/codified" xmlns:codify="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/codify" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <num>42-3404.16</num>
  <heading proof="needed">Unlawful acts.</heading>
  <para>
    <num undesignated="true">(a)</num>
    <text>It shall be unlawful for any person to:</text>
    <para>
      <num>(1)</num>
      <text>Coerce a tenant or tenant organization to waive their rights under <cite path="42|34|IV">this subchapter</cite>;</text>
    </para>
    <para>
      <num>(2)</num>
      <text>Retaliate against or harass a tenant seeking to exercise their rights under <cite path="42|34|IV">this subchapter</cite>; or</text>
    </para>
    <para>
      <num>(3)</num>
      <text>Make fraudulent or misleading statements or engage in conduct intended to prevent a tenant from exercising their rights under <cite path="42|34|IV">this subchapter</cite>.</text>
    </para>
  </para>
